- You know what I mean.

35:19.680 --> 35:21.557
I told you to speak to him.

35:21.640 --> 35:24.200
You told me to be nice to him.

35:26.040 --> 35:29.828
What you fucking talking about? Eh?

35:32.920 --> 35:34.273
Oh, no!

35:36.360 --> 35:38.749
Tell... tell me you didn't...

35:40.600 --> 35:42.033
It was your idea.

35:42.120 --> 35:43.553
No. No.

35:44.440 --> 35:47.079
Don't touch me. Don't come near me.

35:47.160 --> 35:53.474
You... upstairs? In my own house?
For fucking benefits?

35:53.560 --> 35:55.437
Benefits, Monica?

35:55.520 --> 35:58.830
Even prossies have the sense of mind
to do it for cold, hard cash...

35:58.920 --> 36:02.071
- Don't you dare turn this round!
- Don't you fucking start!

36:02.160 --> 36:04.879
You told me!
This is what you wanted!

36:04.960 --> 36:07.713
Oh, oh, yeah, yeah...
Of course it is(!)

36:07.800 --> 36:09.950
Of course it is.
Yeah, this is what I wanted(!)

36:10.040 --> 36:13.749
16 years of age, the world
unfurling at me feet, I said,

36:13.840 --> 36:19.278
"Hey, what I want is nine kids, a house
that's falling apart around me,

36:19.360 --> 36:22.750
"a wife who leaves me for another
fucking woman, comes back

36:22.840 --> 36:26.549
"and then fucks around on me again."
Oh, yeah, this is what I wanted!

36:26.640 --> 36:27.993
Don't... Fuck off!

36:32.120 --> 36:37.353
Yeah, I was on me knees, praying, "Oh,
please, grant my wish, your Almighty."

36:37.440 --> 36:39.829
And He did!

36:42.760 --> 36:46.196
I mean, this is heaven... with you.

36:46.280 --> 36:50.159
Every day, every second,
every breath.

36:50.240 --> 36:52.549
This is fucking heaven, this is!

37:05.280 --> 37:08.636
I did it for you.
I did it for the family.

37:08.720 --> 37:10.392
Don't, Mon.

37:10.480 --> 37:13.153
Just... just don't.

37:14.880 --> 37:18.316
From now on, Monica...

37:19.920 --> 37:22.957
...just don't.

37:25.760 --> 37:27.910
All right?

37:39.560 --> 37:40.913
It's OK, Paddy.

37:41.000 --> 37:42.558
It's OK. You're safe.

37:45.040 --> 37:47.395
Oh, Mimi. I'm so sorry...

37:47.480 --> 37:49.789
Sssh. Everything's going
to be all right.

37:49.880 --> 37:52.440
No, Mimi, no. I got lost.

37:52.520 --> 37:55.034
I was stupid and I have to change.

37:55.120 --> 37:59.716
This life we lead, this world of ours...
Something's gotta give!

37:59.800 --> 38:01.836
I forgot.

38:01.920 --> 38:05.276
I forgot just how much
you meant to me...

38:08.720 --> 38:10.392
I love you so fucking much...

38:10.480 --> 38:13.392
I know, Paddy. I know.

38:13.480 --> 38:15.311
I don't even...

38:15.400 --> 38:17.709
I don't even remember how I got here.

38:18.840 --> 38:21.957
They found you by the side
of the road, half dead.

38:24.240 --> 38:25.798
Better let them see to you.

38:25.880 --> 38:28.314
Need to tell the boys
you're awake as well.

38:28.400 --> 38:29.276
Mimi...

38:33.080 --> 38:35.435
NURSE WHISTLES

38:35.520 --> 38:40.514
SHE WHISTLES: Bad Guys
from Bugsy Malone

38:43.440 --> 38:46.591
<i>No-o-o-o-o-ol</i>

38:53.440 --> 38:55.158
I think it's time now, Patrick.

39:05.360 --> 39:06.873
PIANO INTRO

39:06.960 --> 39:11.317
♪ We could have been anything
that we wanted to be... ♪

39:11.400 --> 39:14.949
SINGING CONTINUES

39:24.600 --> 39:26.750
My daughter, Patrick.

39:26.840 --> 39:28.398
Rachel.

39:28.480 --> 39:30.630
