39:37.720 --> 39:39.073
Maureen...

39:39.160 --> 39:41.116
Only 18 years old.

39:41.200 --> 39:43.395
18 years...

39:43.480 --> 39:45.630
that's nothing.

39:45.720 --> 39:47.358
And the worst thing is,

39:47.440 --> 39:51.797
I went to the police, and even if
they did manage to make it stick...

39:52.960 --> 39:54.871
...well, you'd be out long before that.

39:54.960 --> 39:58.669
I'll stop. Swear to God, I'll stop.

39:58.760 --> 40:00.876
Even if I believed you,

40:00.960 --> 40:04.509
it wouldn't change anything.

40:04.600 --> 40:07.114
We have to be accountable...

40:07.200 --> 40:09.350
for our choices...

40:10.840 --> 40:13.195
...for what we've done.

40:13.280 --> 40:16.352
(Kids) # We could have been anything
that we wanted to be... #

40:20.120 --> 40:21.712
Oh, no, no, no, no!

40:21.800 --> 40:25.270
- Not that, please!
- I was a nurse. It's all right, Patrick.

40:25.360 --> 40:27.874
- I know what I'm doing.
- No, no...! Fuck off!

40:27.960 --> 40:29.188
Get off, no!

40:30.720 --> 40:32.756
It's better if you please stay still.

40:32.840 --> 40:35.991
Argh! No!

40:36.080 --> 40:37.399
That's it.

40:38.960 --> 40:42.999
Maybe it would be a good idea
for you to try your product.

40:43.080 --> 40:47.790
After all, you didn't have issues
with anyone else trying it, did you?

